    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The CFD hemolysis model meets all required credibility factor levels for Model Risk Level 2 at the Medium assurance level. Seven factors were formally assessed and all achieved their required levels. Six factors were appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. A known limitation exists in the form of turbulence model under-performance at the low-flow operating point (2.5 L/min), which produced a 31% over-prediction of RHI in validation. This limitation is acknowledged. The decision is Accepted.",
